                    <h3 class="brutus-text-title">Simon dos Reis Spedsbjerg</h3>
                    <p>MSc Software Engineer</p>
                    <p>
                        I’ve always gravitated toward stealth gameplay back in the early Assassin’s Creed days, I was among the few who would fully commit to sneaking rather than charging in, and I still play that way today in titles like Cyberpunk 2077. I’m also a long-time fan of Paradox Interactive’s grand strategy games, which fuel my love for depth and careful planning. Unfortunately, truly great stealth games remain rare, and that’s part of what motivates this project: to create experiences where players must think several steps ahead while constantly feeling the tension of being hunted—never quite knowing if the “giant troll next door” might catch their scent.
                    </p>
